<sect2>
<title>Introduction to <application>udftools</application></title>

<para>The <application>udftools</application> package contains utilities
for creating and mounting <acronym>CD-RW</acronym> disks with
<acronym>udf</acronym> file systems for both
reading and writing. <acronym>Udf</acronym> files ystems are used on
both <acronym>CD-RW</acronym> media and
on <acronym>DVD</acronym>.  For more details of the udf filesystem standard see:
<ulink url="http://www.osta.org"/> and <ulink
url="http://www.ecma-international.org"/>.</para>

